  "title": "Delivery Driver",
  "description": "<h4>Job description</h4>\n<ul>\n  <li>Ensure deliveries are done in a timely manner.</li>\n  <li>Assists in department daily routine.</li>\n  <li>Perform good customer service.</li>\n  <li>Loading and unloading of goods.</li>\n  <li>Adhere to SOP for delivery.</li>\n  <li>Ad hoc duties that are assigned from time to time.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Entry level candidates are welcome</li>\n  <li>Minimum GCE 'O' Levels or ITE / Diploma / Professional Certification in Administration are welcome to apply.</li>\n  <li>Willing to learn with good attitude.</li>\n  <li>Organized and responsible.</li>\n  <li>Valid Class 3 driving license.</li>\n  <li>Salary will be commensurate based on experience and qualifications.</li>\n</ul>",
